title: Group Therapy: The Co-Worker That Doesn't Leave Her Alone
description: A listeners started a new job and loves it except for one co-worker.  The co-worker bothers her all the time, texts her and if she doesn't text back asks what's wrong, and it's become too much to the point that she's starting to dislike her job.  She needs advice on what to do about it!
